Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.70,0:00:04.44,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.50,0:00:06.70,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.18,0:00:12.98,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我赐予的恩惠还没有消失
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.46,0:00:23.92,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}燃尽吧 外法之业
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.28,0:00:25.48,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}Will All Wisp
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.70,0:00:03.70,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.08,0:02:34.88,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.08,0:02:33.24,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:35.48,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}一瞬间全部消灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.22,0:02:37.68,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}令人惊叹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.64,0:02:39.56,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}出发
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.46,0:02:42.38,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}亚丝菲·阿尔·安朵美达
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.84,0:02:44.38,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}伟大的物品制作者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.90,0:02:47.34,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}第二名字是“万能者”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.30,0:02:49.42,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}而且那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.92,0:02:51.70,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}行事犹如疾风
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.30,0:03:00.94,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.46,0:03:05.64,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}塌方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.08,0:03:20.12,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这 这是…贝尔的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.24,0:03:36.28,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}已经离开这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.16,0:03:41.20,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}在此地失去多数装备后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.68,0:03:45.98,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}身负重伤的他们徘徊于黑暗地下城的可能性微乎其微
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.16,0:03:51.22,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}会做出如此愚蠢选择的团队早就被全部消灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.74,0:03:58.78,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}如此一来 他们只能选择放弃回地面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.24,0:04:03.18,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}铤而走险下潜至第18层安全地带
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.00,0:04:07.20,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}地下城有无数竖坑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.02,0:04:11.54,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}与其回上层 不如下潜来得更有效率
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:14.28,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}即便如此…下潜？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.66,0:04:16.54,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}他们疯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.62,0:04:17.66,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}换做我的话 会那么做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.74,0:04:19.80,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}所以他们也会…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.60,0:04:24.52,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不 曾经历过一次冒险的他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.96,0:04:26.76,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}应该会选择继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.92,0:04:29.78,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我也支持这种看法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.84,0:04:31.68,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.90,0:04:35.04,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我感觉到 贝尔在下面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.66,0:04:38.66,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}决定了 我们赶去第18层
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.34,0:04:43.42,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}一定要平安无事 贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:50.50,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔赫 贝尔赫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:52.66,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}精力枯竭？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.26,0:04:54.40,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}莉莉 贝尔赫他…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:56.20,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.62,0:06:11.20,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}差不多该给我一个解释了吧 荷米斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.68,0:06:14.10,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你打算救贝尔的那个理由
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.50,0:06:17.78,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我不是告诉你了嘛 为了救挚友…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.84,0:06:19.14,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}少糊弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.34,0:06:25.10,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}某位大人物拜托我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.42,0:06:28.10,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}派我前来确认一下贝尔的状况
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.98,0:06:30.24,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}某位大人物？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.52,0:06:35.90,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}但也不至于拜托我来这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:38.96,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我也对贝尔产生了兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.78,0:06:43.32,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我想要亲眼见证以及看清楚 赫斯缇亚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.24,0:06:48.62,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}他是否适合肩负这个时代的重任
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:53.00,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}坚持住…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.26,0:07:10.08,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这就是…悲叹之大壁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.80,0:07:21.62,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}怪物Goraiyasu的话 应该已经被远征的洛基眷族消灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:24.78,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}考虑到间隔恢复时间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.34,0:07:27.30,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}现在还勉强来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.38,0:08:04.52,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}快跑 快跑 快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.16,0:08:08.76,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}快跑 快跑 快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.88,0:08:21.02,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}快跑…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.38,0:08:31.12,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}莉莉 贝尔赫 神明大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.44,0:08:51.34,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}请你…救救…我的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:53.78,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我的同伴…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.26,0:09:08.26,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.76,0:09:10.48,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}莉莉 贝尔赫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.48,0:09:12.70,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.16,0:09:18.86,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不碍事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.86,0:09:22.34,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}艾丝小姐 你为什么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.56,0:09:27.74,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}洛基眷族远征归途中 恰巧暂时扎营在第18层
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.88,0:09:29.20,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}第18层？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.22,0:09:31.74,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我的同伴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.22,0:09:41.48,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔赫 莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.32,0:09:49.36,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}他们也没事 黎贝利亚替他们治疗过了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.46,0:09:52.36,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你的伤势也很严重
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.36,0:09:56.50,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}真的很感谢您 出手搭救了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.50,0:09:59.32,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不用谢 你现在已经能动了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:00.46,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:05.64,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}团长吩咐我一旦你们苏醒便要去通知他们 你也和我一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.56,0:10:12.90,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}初次征战中层区域 一下子就跑去第18层了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:16.00,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}能成功逃离阶层主 干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:21.20,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不 其实…是我们运气好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.40,0:10:26.48,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这次承蒙各位搭救 真的非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.58,0:10:30.72,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}明白了 我们会把你们当作客人款待的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.72,0:10:34.02,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}抱歉 麻烦您为我们做的这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.36,0:10:39.76,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我如果敢对艾丝的朋友见死不救 她会怨恨我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.78,0:10:49.78,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}其实队内有数人中了怪物难以医治的剧毒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.00,0:10:53.44,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}正派腿脚快的同伴回地面取解药
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.76,0:10:57.64,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我们打算扎营到解药送来为止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.28,0:11:02.14,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}真的是Argonaut君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:03.88,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这次辛苦你了 艾丝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.88,0:11:05.36,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}缇欧娜 缇欧涅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.36,0:11:08.90,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你终于醒了 太好了 Argonaut君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.90,0:11:12.10,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}请问 Argonaut是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.34,0:11:17.46,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}别理她 这傻瓜帮你胡乱取的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.64,0:11:22.84,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我们碰巧见到你对付米诺陶洛斯的情景
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:27.74,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}于是让我回想起小时候喜欢的童话故事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.24,0:11:30.24,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.40,0:11:36.30,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}能去中层区也就意味着你已经升级至Lv2了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:40.16,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}居然能制服米诺陶洛斯 你干得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.16,0:11:42.38,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.82,0:11:46.58,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}脸红了 真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.98,0:11:51.32,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那是…应该…该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.09,0:12:09.11,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.15,0:12:12.61,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}没事 只不过这里是地下城吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.25,0:12:14.91,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}为什么会出现这样的光亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.81,0:12:26.25,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}好壮观
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.65,0:12:32.03,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.59,0:12:35.21,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}嗯 全部都是水晶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.63,0:12:38.01,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}时间慢慢流逝 光芒就会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.17,0:12:40.19,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这里就迎来了夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:50.85,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}冒险者们称之为迷宫之乐园 Under Resort
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.45,0:13:01.21,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}真的变暗了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.13,0:13:09.17,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这里是哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.67,0:13:11.29,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.61,0:13:13.21,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}莉莉 贝尔赫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.21,0:13:15.29,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你们没事吧 还认识我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.47,0:13:20.49,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我认不出贝尔大人 那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.79,0:13:26.43,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}嗯 既然能听见莉莉的啰嗦 我也应该没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.67,0:13:32.95,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}实在抱歉 贝尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.27,0:13:36.71,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我们拖累了你 是我们不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:38.87,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}没…没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.87,0:13:42.97,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}要是没有莉莉 我们不可能考虑下潜到第18层
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.97,0:13:46.43,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}要是没有贝尔赫 我们早被地狱犬的火焰烧死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.43,0:13:50.69,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}正因为有你们 有这支团队 我们才能逃过这一劫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.61,0:13:52.51,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.79,0:13:56.45,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}看来我们三人缺一不可
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.93,0:13:59.71,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}饭菜准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.01,0:14:02.19,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你们没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.87,0:14:04.51,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}剑姬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.75,0:14:06.85,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}艾丝·华伦斯坦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.29,0:14:15.55,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}他们是为了同伴而愿意舍身相救 才得以到达第18层的勇敢冒险者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:19.97,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}同为冒险者的我们该心怀敬意招待他们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.53,0:14:25.37,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}给你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.69,0:14:28.89,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}呃…这是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.55,0:14:32.07,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}在第18层采摘的水果
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.07,0:14:34.39,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}地下城居然还有水果？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.15,0:14:41.67,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔大人 贝尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.67,0:14:44.07,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}若不合您胃口 请给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.65,0:14:45.51,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}给你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.63,0:14:50.91,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}这个味道确实太甜了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.13,0:14:58.97,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}Argonaut君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.49,0:15:02.95,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}告诉我 要怎么做才能将所有能力值达到S呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.95,0:15:05.37,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}慢慢告诉我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.87,0:15:29.67,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我没听说会遇到那么庞大的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.11,0:15:31.31,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}疼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:41.01,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}神明大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.41,0:15:47.63,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔 贝尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.63,0:15:49.35,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}神明大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.55,0:15:50.65,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.49,0:15:54.71,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}真的是本人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.73,0:15:56.01,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}神明大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.65,0:16:01.27,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.59,0:16:04.23,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}神明大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.17,0:16:18.09,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}抱歉 害你担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.05,0:16:25.31,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}该适可而止了 赫斯缇雅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.31,0:16:28.53,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我说你 别打扰我们久别重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.53,0:16:30.73,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔大人是为保护我而受伤的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.73,0:16:32.87,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}眼下必须静养
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.23,0:16:37.01,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}华伦斯坦某某 为什么连你也在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.01,0:16:39.93,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10\pos(640,53)}等等 在听我说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.73,0:16:41.21,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}克朗尼先生 您平安无事太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.21,0:16:42.69,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}琉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.87,0:16:45.77,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你就是贝尔克朗尼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.89,0:16:47.39,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.45,0:16:49.43,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是吗 原来就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.51,0:16:51.43,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}非常想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.61,0:16:54.93,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我的名字是荷米斯 请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.27,0:16:57.29,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.29,0:17:00.29,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不客气 为了好友赫斯缇雅才这么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.39,0:17:04.13,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}如果要感谢 就感谢除了我之外的他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:08.29,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}多亏有他们在 我们才能安全到达这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.61,0:17:20.47,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.47,0:17:22.55,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}怎么会呢 请不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.55,0:17:25.47,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}就算你怎么道歉 我也不可能轻易原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.51,0:17:27.45,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我们差点赔上性命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.45,0:17:30.61,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}没错 不能这样轻易当没事发生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.05,0:17:33.91,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}真的非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.31,0:17:36.91,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我能理解莉莉你们的愤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.13,0:17:38.93,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我甘愿接受惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.93,0:17:40.73,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}要怪就怪我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.25,0:17:43.03,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那是我下的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.83,0:17:48.17,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}直到现在 我依然觉得那个指示没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.17,0:17:52.57,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你还有脸当着我们的面说这种话 大男人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.11,0:18:07.23,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我也一样 如果关乎到贝尔赫和莉莉同伴性命的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.07,0:18:10.81,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}也许我也会做同样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.43,0:18:16.55,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}既然贝尔大人这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.67,0:18:18.15,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.67,0:18:20.65,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}但并非表示我认同你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.65,0:18:23.09,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}嗯 那就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.85,0:18:28.89,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那么接下来讨论今后的安排吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.33,0:18:30.29,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}亚丝菲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.73,0:18:32.89,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}首先有关回地面的事宜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:37.63,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我们将会等洛基眷族击败Goraiyasu后出发
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.97,0:18:42.59,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}然后他们来回赶路与我们汇合最快也需要2天时间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.85,0:18:45.59,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}所以 有一天的空闲时间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.01,0:18:49.25,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}难得有时间 明天好好休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.51,0:18:56.73,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔大人 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.73,0:18:58.27,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}嗯 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.41,0:19:05.05,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔赫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.01,0:19:10.75,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}赫菲斯托丝拜托我交给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.07,0:19:15.29,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}还有传话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.45,0:19:39.73,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}没想到这里也属于地下城
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.03,0:19:42.95,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.85,0:19:47.77,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}其实…有点睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.17,0:19:53.25,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}请问艾丝小姐为什么来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.75,0:19:56.13,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}因为看见你走过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.25,0:20:01.37,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}有点担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:04.47,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}妨碍到你了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.47,0:20:06.65,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不 才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.65,0:20:09.09,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}太开心了 也不对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.07,0:20:12.77,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}贝尔总是那么紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.83,0:20:21.09,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}什么时候出发
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.27,0:20:24.15,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}呃…在艾丝小姐你们之后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.29,0:20:27.11,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}打算明天一天好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.11,0:20:27.99,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.39,0:20:30.21,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}那么你想逛逛城市吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.25,0:20:33.47,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}地下城里还有城市？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.27,0:20:35.61,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}明天想去逛逛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.61,0:20:37.11,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}非常想去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.11,0:20:41.17,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}城市吗 到底是什么样的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.89,0:20:43.47,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}城市吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.19,0:20:47.01,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}你真见外 贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.21,0:20:50.83,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}要去的话 为何不直接邀请我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.85,0:20:57.03,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我和贝尔 难道不应该是我们两个去吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.09,0:20:59.17,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.85,0:21:05.63,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}所以华伦某某君 不经我同意不许你邀请贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.63,0:21:10.11,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}约会之类的绝对不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.45,0:21:14.17,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}约会？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.17,0:21:18.03,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}不是 你误解了 神明大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.03,0:21:19.87,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}约会是什么鬼！贝尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.15,0:21:21.21,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10\pos(640,53)}又跑出来了 你这只偷腥猫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.93,0:09:19.33,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.47,0:23:09.15,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}我再也不会打造魔剑了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.47,0:23:10.51,DXC-main,,0,0,0,fx,{\blur10}是吗
